
tarāsh kar mire baazū uḌaan chhoḌ gayā 
havā ke paas barahna kamān chhoḌ gayā 
rafāqatoñ kā mirī us ko dhyān kitnā thā 
zamīn le lī magar āsmān chhoḌ gayā 
ajiib shaḳhs thā bārish kā rañg dekh ke bhī 
khule darīche pe ik pūl-dān chhoḌ gayā 
jo bādaloñ se bhī mujh ko chhupā.e rakhtā thā 
baḌhī hai dhuup to be-sā.ebān chhoḌ gayā 
nikal gayā kahīñ an-dekhe pāniyoñ kī taraf 
zamīñ ke naam khulā bādbān chhoḌ gayā 
uqaab ko thī ġharaz fāḳhta pakaḌne se 
jo gir ga.ī to yūñhī nīm-jān chhoḌ gayā 
na jaane kaun sā aaseb dil meñ bastā hai 
ki jo bhī Thahrā vo āḳhir makān chhoḌ gayā 
aqab meñ gahrā samundar hai sāmne jañgal 
kis intihā pe mirā mehrbān chhoḌ gayā 